'''洗瓶'''（{{lang-en|Wash Bottle}}）常见于[[實驗室|實驗室]]中，是一種常用於裝[[水|水]]及部分[[有机溶剂|有机溶剂]]的[[容器|容器]]，其外型為帶有{{le|噴嘴|Nozzle}}的{{le|擠瓶|Squeeze bottle}}，在頂蓋上配有[[水管|水管]]型出水口的[[裝置|裝置]]。洗瓶常用於[[溶液|溶液]]的定量轉移、沖洗實驗室各種{{le|實驗室玻璃器皿|Laboratory glassware|玻璃仪器}}如[[試管|試管]]或[[圓底燒瓶|圓底燒瓶]]、或是[[抽滤|抽滤]]等实验操作中。<ref>{{Cite web | language = zh-cn |title=洗瓶 |url=http://www.ulab360.com/prodcat.php?mod=view&id=3858 |access-date=2021-07-22 |website= 佑研匠簇 | archive-date = 2021-04-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210411122554/http://ulab360.com/prodcat.php?mod=view&id=3858 | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | language = zh-tw | title = 高中化學 - 洗瓶 | url = https://www.ehanlin.com.tw/app/keyword/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%AD/%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%B8/%E6%B4%97%E7%93%B6.html | access-date = 2021-07-22 | website = 翰林雲端學院 | archive-date = 2021-07-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210723154558/https://www.ehanlin.com.tw/app/keyword/%E9%AB%98%E4%B8%AD/%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%B8/%E6%B4%97%E7%93%B6.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>洗瓶中常見的是擠壓型，頂部會用螺旋蓋密封。當用手對瓶身施加壓力時，裡面的液體會因為增壓而從噴嘴中擠成一條狹窄的液體流噴出瓶外。<ref name = "Fisher">{{Cite web | language = en |title=Wash Bottles|url=https://www.fishersci.com/us/en/browse/90094131/wash-bottles |access-date=2021-07-20 |website=Fisher Sci. | archive-date = 2020-08-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200811131534/https://www.fishersci.com/us/en/browse/90094131/wash-bottles | dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | language = en | title = Wash Bottles | url = https://prezi.com/jtfjmgjviptu/test-tube-brush/?frame=4ce9fbc27a89de92d261eafe82b75a3a55ece029 | access-date = 2021-07-22 | website = Prezi | archive-date = 2021-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210722062837/https://prezi.com/jtfjmgjviptu/test-tube-brush/?frame=4ce9fbc27a89de92d261eafe82b75a3a55ece029 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 材質 ==
大多數洗瓶由[[聚乙烯|聚乙烯]]製成，聚乙烯是一種柔軟的耐溶劑性石油基塑料。<ref>{{Cite web | language = en |title=Low Density Polyethylene (LDPE) Labware |url=https://www.thermofisher.com/tw/zt/home/life-science/lab-plasticware-supplies/plastic-material-selection/low-density-polyethylene-ldpe-labware.html |access-date=2021-07-20|website=Termo Fisher | archive-date = 2021-07-22 | archive-url = https://archive.ph/daDdO | dead-url = no}}</ref>洗瓶通常會包含一個內部汲取管，讓瓶身在直立時仍可使用。根據使用者進行工作的需求，可以依靠洗瓶來裝滿一系列常見的實驗室[[溶劑|溶劑]]及[[反應物|試劑]]。這些溶液包括[[纯净水|去離子水]]、[[清潔劑|清潔溶液]]或是沖洗溶劑等，如[[丙酮|丙酮]]、[[異丙醇|異丙醇]]、[[乙醇|乙醇]]等有機溶劑。另外在生物實驗室中，通常會準備[[次氯酸鈉|次氯酸鈉]]溶液保存在洗瓶中備用，以便能隨時消毒不需要的培養物。<ref>{{Cite web | language = en | title = Wash Bottle | url = https://stemcelltulsa.com/products/wash-bottle | access-date = 2021-07-20 | website = The Stemcell Science Shop | archive-date = 2021-07-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210720151521/https://stemcelltulsa.com/products/wash-bottle | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 顏色標記 == 
在洗瓶上的顏色標記有一套一致的規範，該標記主要用於識別洗瓶的內容物，同時也可避免使用者誤用溶劑。紅色的標記代表內容物為[[丙酮|丙酮]]，白色可代表為[[乙醇|乙醇]]、[[次氯酸鈉|次氯酸鈉]]、或是[[蒸餾水|蒸餾水]]，綠色代表[[甲醇|甲醇]]，黃色代表[[異丙醇|異丙醇]]，藍色則僅代表蒸餾水。<ref>{{Cite web | language = en | title = Chimactiv - Interactive numerical educational resources for the analysis of complex media | url = http://chimactiv.agroparistech.fr/en/bases/materiel/materiel/28# | access-date = 2021-03-15 | website = chimactiv.agroparistech.fr | archive-date = 2021-07-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210722074441/http://chimactiv.agroparistech.fr/en/bases/materiel/materiel/28 | dead-url = no }}</ref>也有洗瓶會標示[[NFPA_704|NFPA 704]]警示菱形符號，讓使用者能識別在使用該洗瓶時，能得知其內含物的健康危害性及化學特性，以及使用時建議配備的防護衣或設備。<ref>{{Cite web | language = en |title=GHS Labeled Wash Bottles|url=https://www.bac-online.com/products/Shop%20Supplies/Bottles%20and%20Sprayers/GHS%20Labeled%20Wash%20Bottles.aspx |access-date=2021-07-20 |website=Business Aircraft Consumables Inc. | archive-date = 2020-11-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201124091059/https://www.bac-online.com/products/Shop%20Supplies/Bottles%20and%20Sprayers/GHS%20Labeled%20Wash%20Bottles.aspx | dead-url = no}}</ref>

== 安全性 ==
洗瓶上有時也會有安全警告標籤，用於識別潛在的危險。<ref>{{Cite web | language = en |title= Right to Know, Safety-Vented Wash Bottles with GHS Labeling|url=https://www.belart.com/media/catalogstudio/FAQS/GHS%20Wash%20Bottles.pdf |access-date=2021-07-20|website=Bel-Art | archive-date = 2021-07-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210720151522/https://www.belart.com/media/catalogstudio/FAQS/GHS%20Wash%20Bottles.pdf | dead-url = no}}</ref>在洗瓶蓋子上另有一個小的壓力釋放孔，當瓶內裝有高[[蒸汽壓|蒸汽壓]]試劑（例如[[乙醇|乙醇]]或[[甲醇|甲醇]]）的情況下，可以依靠該小孔釋放過量的蒸汽壓，同時可避免試劑在不使用時會透過噴嘴噴濺出瓶外。<ref name = "Fisher"/><ref>{{Cite report | language = en |last1=Schmitt |first1=C. R. |last2= Whitehead |first2=H. D. |last3= White |first3=J. E. |title=Evaluation of Wash Bottles for Flammable Solvent Use |url=https://www.osti.gov/servlets/purl/6035473 |year=1979 |access-date=2021-07-20 |publisher= Oak Ridge Y-12 Plant |website= OSTI.GOV |location=United States |osti= 6035473 |doi= 10.2172/6035473 | archive-date = 2018-07-25 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180725184701/https://www.osti.gov/biblio/6035473 | dead-url = no}}</ref>

=== 優勢 ===
洗瓶的使用有助於研究人員能量測及控制所用液體的精確量，避免浪費過量液體或使用量不足等。此外，不需要的雜質或顆粒不能穿透至洗瓶，避免瓶內的液體被汙染。<ref>{{cite journal | language = en |last1=Woodrift|first1=Ray|title=A Convenient Type of Wash Bottle|journal= Journal of Chemical Education|date=1940-07-01|volume=17|issue=7|page=323 |doi=10.1021/ed017p323 |bibcode=1940JChEd..17..323W}}</ref>另外在清潔時，使用洗瓶比使用[[燒杯|燒杯]]或[[量筒|量筒]]更方便。<ref>{{cite journal| language = en |last1=Rudolph|first1=Goetz|title=Wash bottle for volatile solvents | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-chemical-education_1977-10_54_10/page/634 |journal=J. Chem. Educ. |date=1977-10-01|volume=54|issue=10|page=634 |doi=10.1021/ed054p634|bibcode=1977JChEd..54..634G}}</ref>

== 存放方式與種類 ==
洗瓶通常以安全的方式存放在實驗工作臺上，以便能讓使用者輕鬆地找到，並且不會因擺放位置而干擾到正在進行的實驗工作；另外也可透過使用兩個具有相似尺寸的環型[[夾鉗|夾鉗]]連接到格狀桿架上，再將洗瓶放置在夾鉗上。<ref>{{cite journal| language = en |last1=Kjonaas|first1=Richard A.|title=Storage of laboratory wash bottles| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-chemical-education_1984-06_61_6/page/541 |journal= Journal of Chemical Education|date=1984-06-01 |volume=61|issue=6|page=541 |doi=10.1021/ed061p541 |ref=Chemical Education|bibcode=1984JChEd..61..541K}}</ref>

不同類型的洗瓶適用於裝盛不同類型的液體。例如，螺旋氣升式洗瓶（Spiral Gas-lift Wash Bottle）因可去除氣體，適用於存放具有[[溴化物|溴化物]]和[[水|水]][[雙水相系統#兩相|兩相體系]]的混和溶液。<ref>{{cite journal| language = en |last1=B. B.|first1=Corson |title=Absorption efficiency of spiral gas-lift wash bottle|journal=Analytical Chemistry|date=1938-11-01|volume=10|issue=11|page=646| doi=10.1021/ac50127a015}}</ref>此外，一個擁有簡單刻度的洗瓶有助於使用者能夠得知使用的液體量。<ref>{{cite journal| language = en |last1=Earle R.|first1=Caley |title=Simple graduated wash bottles|journal=Analytical Chemistry|date=1929-07-01|volume=1|issue=3|page=162 |doi=10.1021/ac50067a027}}</ref>Nalgene Teflon FEP 洗瓶在製作上使用了特殊類型的塑料，可以用來儲存一些如強溶劑或腐蝕性物質等溶液。<ref>{{cite journal| language = en |last1=|first1=|title=Nalgene® Wash Bottles|journal=Analytical Chemistry|date=1973-10-01|volume=45|issue=12|page=980A |doi=10.1021/ac60334a720}}</ref>

